  <lyrics>[V1]
 /Kawsayniyta qopusaj Señor Jesusniyman,
 Cruzpi Pay noqapaj wañorqa./
 
[C]
 /Cristo cruzpi wañuspa, kawsayta qowarqa,
 Perdonawarqatajjuchayta./
 
[V2]
 /Jesusniypa chakisninman chimpaykushajtiy,
 Juchasniyta llimphuchawarqa./
 
[V3]
 /Juchaykiwan, amigóy, Diosman chimpaykuwaj.
 Pay muñan qanta salvasuyta./
 
</lyrics></song>